{"tid":822662,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"XS、XS Max、XR 小米官網有份賣？","createTime":"2018-09-16T12:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T17:26:12.000Z","uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eadd10afa640c1dae1e424dba93f028e06d3ceb4","tid":822662,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"XS、XS Max、XR 小米官網有份賣？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/202718_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F202718_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a8390fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\niPhone 人人搶，連小米都要賣埋一份？<br />\n<br />\n小米中國官網在新 iPhone 系列推出時，也分別上架了 XS、XS Max 以及 XR，唔通上了市的小米真係咁把炮，連 iPhone 都賣埋一份？答案當然唔係啦！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/202727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F202727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=488fe10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n其實小米今次開賣的，是XS、XS Max 以及 XR「套餐」，代表用 iPhone XS 的機價，可以買到咩小米產品而已，以賣得最高的 XS Max 為例，9599 人民幣就可以買到小米8 128GB + 小米筆記本Pro + 小米藍牙項圈耳機 + 小米手環3，除了促銷自家產品之外，也有諷刺 iPhone 賣得貴的意味。"},{"pid":"46f0fc4518feeae0044210821528c76cd2ef6ccd","tid":822662,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43189d27a3053d31914e86765c46f12c09fbcc5d","tid":822662,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"46f0fc4518feeae0044210821528c76cd2ef6ccd","tid":822662,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"eadd10afa640c1dae1e424dba93f028e06d3ceb4","tid":822662,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"XS、XS Max、XR 小米官網有份賣？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\